      <para id="id68543">During the first 8 seconds the car had a positive acceleration. This means that its velocity increased. The velocity is positive so the car is speeding up.
During the next 6 seconds the car had a negative acceleration. This means that its velocity decreased. The velocity is negative so the car is slowing down. </para>
      </item> </list> </solution>
